---
title: Ginger & Hoisin-Glazed Tofu with Pear Slaw & Sesame Fries
description: Sweet and salty hoisin sauce to drizzle over golden tofu steaks is a great combination. Try serving with sesame fries and you’ve got another match. Putting sweet pear in a creamy slaw and adding it to the ensemble is yet one more amazing flavour combo. Altogether that's one stellar dish that everyone is going to be raving about.

